@NODE MAIN "Onda 2.x"
                                @{b}@{u}Onda v2@{uu}@{ub}

                             algrecc@tin.it
                         @{fg fill}© 2002 Alberto Grecchi@{fg shadow}

Onda isn't a paint program like DPaint because it hasn't the classic tools
for the paint such as lines and circles.

It's not a graphic program 3D.

With this program it's possible to create quickly particular animations in the
GIF ANIM format for a suitable use in the WEB pages.




