@NODE Requirements " Requirements "

@{b}@{u}SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS@{uu}@{ub}

Onda requires:

Amiga OS 3.0 or better

Multiview in SYS:Utilities/ for the guide

Processor 020..060






        @{"    Installation   " LINK Installation}

        @{"       Usage       " LINK Usage}
