        @{"      Author       " LINK Author}
@ENDNODE


@NODE Commands " Commands "

@{b}@{u}COMMANDS@{uu}@{ub}

Load............allows to read from the harddisk a image in the IFF format
                max 150 x 150 256 colours.
Wave type.......it's the effect type to apply to the loaded image.

Accuracy........calculation accuracy, this affects only some effects, by
                setting it to the minimum allows to have a fast preview
                of the result.
Level...........controls the amplitude of the effect applyed to the image.

BackGround......if enabled by setting it ON will be always used the original
                image as background, in the fact the frames are drawed on
                the image itself.

